import React from 'react'
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Switch, Route } from 'react-router-dom'
import { Navbar, Sidebar, Footer, ProductDetails, SecondNavbar } from './components'
import {
  Home,
  SingleProduct,
  Cart,
  Error,
  FormAccepting,
} from './pages'

function App() {
  return (
  
      <Router>
        <Navbar />
        <Sidebar />

        <Switch>
          <Route exact path='/'>
            <Home />
          </Route>
          <Route path='/cart'>
            <Cart />
          </Route>

<Route path="/checkout">
<FormAccepting />
</Route>




<Route path="/prdetail">
<ProductDetails />
</Route>

          <Route path='/products/:id' children={<SingleProduct />} />
          <Route path='*'>
            <Error />
          </Route>
        </Switch>
        <Footer />
      </Router>
  
  )
}

export default App
